data.chText: （尤指被视为有序体系时的）宇宙
data.enText: the universe, especially when it is thought of as an ordered system

means: (尤指被视为有序体系时的)宇宙

example: they study the evolution of the universe

tr: any of various mostly Mexican herbs of the genus Cosmos having radiate heads of variously colored flowers and pinnate leaves

partsOfSpeech.dec: cosm 世界，宇宙 + ic …的 → 宇宙的
cosmo 世界，宇宙 + polis 城市 → 世界性城市 → 国际都市
macro 大，宏大 + cosm 世界，宇宙 → 宏观世界
micro 小，微小 + cosm 世界，宇宙 → 微观世界
